overview: Bar Wrestling 4: Autumn In LA BAR Wrestling’s fourth event, Autumn in LA, is a women’s showcase that boasts one of the best main events the company has produced thus far. This event was held on September 7, 2017. Amazing Kong vs Taya Valkyrie Chelsea Green & Ivy Quinn vs Katarina Leigh & Scarlett Bordeaux  Christina Von Erie vs Shotzi Blackheart  Heather Monroe vs Ruby Raze Brian Cage, Eli Drake, Hot Young Briley & Joey Ryan vs Ethan Carter III, JTG, Luchasaurus & X-Pac Candice Le Rae vs Tessa Blanchard  You can get this event on DVD or Blu Ray at Highspots.com  Also streaming at Highspots Wrestling Network
title: Bar Wrestling 4: Autumn In LA
